      "message": "The need is to be able to have 2 different exception types to distinguish between client and server errors.\n\nIf we are keeping NcompException as super type, it is then required to have 2 different sub types (DmiRequestException and ServerNcmpException).\n\nIf the common super type is not used, this is the one we could eventually get rid of.",
